.net/upload/2017/11/18/114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg&h=3ad3c678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我公司都有請輕度弱智人士<br />\n做茶水and抹下台，寄下信，搬下重野<br />\n比最低工資<br />\n<br />\n唔好歧視人"},{"pid":"3f9e12248229e266e0d342d9ac2f760b8baf30a7","tid":472172,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依個世界真係咩垃圾都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你勤力啲做嘢做十年賺二千萬買層一千萬樓自住再買層一千萬租出去，收返2,3萬租一個月，到時咪可以偷下懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10年賺二千萬, 平均月薪15-16萬, 醫生律師都未必搵到, 你個D咩工黎?<br />\n唔好講炒股投資錢搵錢, 實賺ga? 幾多人投資蝕哂成副身家</blockquote><br />\n有料咪做ibank/private bank,冇料咪做sales，大把人揾到"},{"pid":"f874428cda4cba75ee50a243a2c202f0e3f7a6d7","tid":472172,"uid":144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩係白卡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n精神科病歷卡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg&h=3ad3c678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我公司都有請輕度弱智人士<br />\n做茶水and抹下台，寄下信，搬下重野<br />\n比最低工資<br />\n<br />\n唔好歧視人</blockquote><br />\n老竇搵緊七皮 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2f6ed7881aefd9e44d4545bdc6365190eb8ad8","tid":472172,"uid":33643,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":