,3萬租一個月，到時咪可以偷下懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪就係拎緊白卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未出嚟做嘢，不過屋企有錢，白咭留返你地成家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都唔明白屋企人有錢 點解你都可以拎黎打飛機<br />\n 睇你d言辭 我諗你真係極度自滿既人 <br />\n不過你離開左你屋企 你乜鳩都唔係 咪撚咁戇鳩喇"},{"pid":"27a6eeb2de9ff760b27a60deed2869c8956d9bb9","tid":472172,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依個世界真係咩垃圾都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你勤力啲做嘢做十年賺二千萬買層一千萬樓自住再買層一千萬租出去，收返2,3萬租一個月，到時咪可以偷下懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪就係拎緊白卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未出嚟做嘢，不過屋企有錢，白咭留返你地成家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都唔明白屋企人有錢 點解你都可以拎黎打飛機<br />\n 睇你d言辭 我諗你真係極度自滿既人 <br />\n不過你離開左你屋企 你乜鳩都唔係 咪撚咁戇鳩喇</blockquote><br />\n純粹唔明點解樓主要諗縮數"},{"pid":"41fc945a73cfc63fda8be274ad9faf29c22e19b1","tid":472172,"uid":64345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩係白卡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n精神科病歷卡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg&h=3ad3c678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我公司都有請輕度弱智人士<br />\n做茶水and抹下台，寄下信，搬下重野<br />\n比最低工資<br />\n<br />\n唔好歧視人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最低工資唔係應份咩。講到自己好優待佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbef085c5ab125b2976eb92429763f5e118bfaac","tid":472172,"uid":40926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"想唔做嘢同想安樂死係兩樣嘢黎，搞清楚先"},{"pid":"ba696b8bf18f830d1ded73d2944abd3c6dca55c3","tid":472172,"uid":154176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依個世界真係咩垃圾都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你勤力啲做嘢做十年賺二千萬買層一千萬樓自住再買層一千萬租出去，收返2,3萬租一個月，到時咪可以偷下懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10年賺二千萬, 平均月薪15-16萬, 醫生律師都未必搵到, 你個D咩工黎?<br />\n唔好講炒股投資錢搵錢, 實賺ga? 幾多人投資蝕哂成副身家</blockquote><br />\n有料咪做ibank/private bank,冇料咪做sales，大把人揾到</blockquote><br />\n係咪又要鬥呀 我一年搵二千萬呀屌你老母<br />\n但我都好唔開心 得唔撚得？"},{"pid":"193733a8101b83ceb6d661dd287789394ad1a186","tid":472172,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依個世界真係咩垃圾都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你勤力啲做嘢做十年賺二千萬買層一千萬樓自住再買層一千萬租出去，收返2,3萬租一個月，到時咪可以偷下懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10年賺二千萬, 平均月薪15-16萬, 醫生律師都未必搵到, 你個D咩工黎?<br />\n唔好講炒股投資錢搵錢, 實賺ga? 幾多人投資蝕哂成副身家</blockquote><br />\n有料咪做ibank/private bank,冇料咪做sales，大把人揾到</blockquote><br />\n係咪又要鬥呀 我一年搵二千萬呀屌你老母<br />\n但我都好唔開心 得唔撚得？</blockquote><br />\n咁你可以死冇人阻你<br />\n但樓主係唔想做嘢喎，咁我叫佢快啲揾夠可以唔做有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d8fbedd3485f8e124fe6099eb849feea4e79ef","tid":472172,"uid":44725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想唔做嘢同想安樂死係兩樣嘢黎，搞清楚先</blockquote><br />\n我希望受到嚴重精神問題引致抑鬱自殺既人可以有安樂死, 係願望黎"},{"pid":"cff94422e70e1a183d1841fe982cb6e68eb73f98","tid":472172,"uid":37447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩係白卡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n精神科病歷卡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F114758_b76c79800d8aff1f286dbbc78e381dad.jpg&h=3ad3c678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真正弱智都上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0faf5ba83957051768cc0d983f742402181d885","tid":472172,"uid":35351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想拎白卡, 因為番工要逼自己做好多唔想做既野, 去滿足其他人對你既期望同要求<br />\n<br />\n為左唔想番工, 曾經多次想自殺, 每日都好大精神壓力, 好希望有安樂死服務</blockquote><br />\n大把人都做緊自己唔想做既野啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c8c6681f832c659d6b259ca82bd202865aff4d","tid":472172,"uid":121885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"做正苦工,轉左PERM再拿白卡,政府就會養你一世俾埋樓你住,坐乜都$2.真係無敵"},{"pid":"049c197a67332fcd98bbb4f174a158b861673d3d","tid":472172,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做正苦工,轉左PERM再拿白卡,政府就會養你一世俾埋樓你住,坐乜都$2.真係無敵</blockquote><br />\nperm咩嚟？"},{"pid":"ae9acab1c932e75487e7ce308b31957bfd5d09ee","tid":472172,"uid":44725,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想拎白卡, 因為番工要逼自己做好多唔想做既野, 去滿足其他人對你既期望同要求<br />\n<br />\n為左唔想番工, 曾經多次想自殺, 每日都好大精神壓力, 好希望有安樂死服務</blockquote><br />\n大把人都做緊自己唔想做既野啦屌<img src=\"/assets/f